---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Sponsors" description="change meta tag">
    <section class="relative isolate px-6 py-24 sm:py-20 lg:px-8">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-x-0 -top-3 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden px-36 blur-3xl"
            aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl prose">
            <h1>Sponsors</h1>

            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-pretty sm:text-xl/8">
                RDD would like to extend our sincerest and warmest thanks to all
                of our 2025 sponsors and look forward to continuing our
                partnership with these excellent companies which support us! We
                urge all of our fans to support those who support us and tell
                them that RDD sent you!
            </p>
            <h2>Become a Sponsor</h2>
            <p>
                As a not-for-profit women's sporting organization, we face
                ongoing challenges in funding our operations, with most of our
                income directed toward practice space and minimal resources for
                operating expenses like guest trainers and bout production. The
                Renegade Derby Dames invite partners to join us in our mission
                through sponsorship, advertising, in-kind donations, and event
                participation. We value collaborations with local businesses and
                aim to support community charities. This season offers a unique
                chance to engage with the rapidly growing sport of roller derby!
                By sponsoring the Renegade Derby Dames, your brand can reach a
                diverse and enthusiastic audience. Our games draw fans from
                across the region, and your partnership will gain visibility
                through social media and promotional materials. Support roller
                derby and connect your brand with an exciting and passionate
                fanbase—let’s make a difference together! You can view our
                Sponsorship Package here! For more information, email us at:
                sponsor @renegadederbydames .com
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>
